Text: A great collection, I have been looking for some of these for quite some time. You can't even *buy* some of these. Sadly, there appears to only be one seed that does not appear to be online. :(
These 2 David Moufang "I.F." albums were the reason I made this torrent series. They are really sublime, and you cannot buy them.  Please seed if you ever get this in full.
